    ⊃(Centered|Font|Spacing)
    ⊙(⊓(□|∘|ColorArg|↥₀|PosArg|≡₀⍚$"_"BoxStrings)
      S!afedbc ≡₀⍚LoadFont⊙⤙⊙⊙∘ ⟜(⍥⋅◡⋅÷₁₀◇≍∞)
    ) # Centered Font Text Pos Size Spacing Color ?
    ≡₀◇(Rayua~DrawTextEx⍥(⍜⊙⋅⋅∘- ◡(÷₂Rayua~MeasureTextEx⊙⊙⋅⊙∘)))
