  ~Square [Centered ← 0] Rect ⊙(⍉↯2 ⍤"Square only takes real numbers, you might intend to use Rect"≠3⊸type) Centered:Centered

  PointOrder ↚ <0/+×⊓+-∩⊸↻₁°⊟≡⊟₃

